These are Puzzles for 3x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-1::.
There are 2 different nationalities: german, polish
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: volleyball, weightlifting
The people use 2 different means of transport: bus, snowmobile
1. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
2. the polish is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |
| Nationality   | polish    | german |
| Sport         | weightlifting | volleyball    |
| Transport     | bus     | snowmobile      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, milk
There are 2 different nationalities: thai, italian
The people use 2 different means of transport: jet-ski, taxi
1. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
2. the thai is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |
| Beverage      | milk  | almond-milk   |
| Nationality   | italian | thai  |
| Transport     | taxi   | jet-ski |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-3::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: filmmaking, board-games
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: epic, western
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: rowing, parkour
1. the person who's hobby is board-games is in an even position##4
2. the person watching epic movies is on the right of the person who's sport is rowing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |
| Hobby         | filmmaking   | board-games  |
| Movie-Genre   | western | epic  |
| Sport         | rowing   | parkour |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-4::.
