The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: scientific, martial-arts
The people use 2 different means of transport: quad-bike, jet-ski
1. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
2. the person eating avocado is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |
| Food          | avocado | lemon |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts   | scientific   |
| Transport     | jet-ski       | quad-bike      |

