.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-7::.
There 2 different types of food: apple, eggplant
The people have 2 different jobs:  bartender, nurse
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: water-polo, handball
1. the person who's sport is handball is on the left of the bartender##1
2. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left or right of the person who's sport is handball##3
3. the person eating apple is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |
| Food    | eggplant | apple     |
| Job     | nurse | bartender |
| Sport   | handball | water-polo    |

 #################################

 
