.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-14::.
There 2 different types of food: mango, cherry
The people have 2 different hobbies: board-games, skydiving
2 different pets are kept: cat, frog
1. the owner of the frog is in an even position##4
2. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the person eating mango##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2      |
| Food    | cherry | mango  |
| Hobby   | skydiving | board-games |
| Pet     | cat  | frog     |

