.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-15::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: photography, sudoku
There are 2 different nationalities: malaysian, turkish
2 different pets are kept: rabbit, fish
1. the owner of the fish is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1
2. the malaysian is on the left of the turkish##1
3. the person who's hobby is photography is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |
| Hobby         | sudoku | photography |
| Nationality   | malaysian     | turkish     |
| Pet           | fish          | rabbit     |

