.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-20::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: crime, animation
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: soul, pop
The people use 2 different means of transport: car, train
1. the person watching crime movies is in an odd position##4
2. the fan of pop is on the right of the person driving the train##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |
| Movie-Genre   | crime | animation |
| Music-Genre   | soul  | pop  |
| Transport     | train | car    |

 